#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/Rendering/WebGPU/README.md:23
msgid ""
"This module uses Dawn's C++ WebGPU implementation on desktop and the "
"`emdawnwebgpu` subcomponent for wasm (automatically fetched by emscripten "
"with `--use-port=emdawnwebgpu` flag)"
