#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/Rendering/WebGPU/README.md:147
msgid ""
"Since WebGPU is already an abstraction over graphics APIs, this module "
"avoids creating another level of abstraction. It leverages WebGPU's C++ "
"flavor for its object-oriented API and RAII. Helper classes in the "
"`vtkWebGPUInternals...` files ensure cleaner bind group initialization code."
msgstr ""

